3,"position":27,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/014_011_029.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":13244,"position":28,"arabic":"فَلْيَتَوَكَّلِ","translation":"ভরসা করা উচিত","audioUrl":"wbw/014_011_030.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":13245,"position":29,"arabic":"ٱلْمُؤْمِنُونَ","translation":"মু’মিনদের","audioUrl":"wbw/014_011_031.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":13246,"position":30,"arabic":"١١","translation":"(১১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":12,"arabic":"وَمَا لَنَآ أَلَّا نَتَوَكَّلَ عَلَى ٱللَّهِ وَقَدْ هَدَىٰنَا سُبُلَنَا ۚ وَلَنَصْبِرَنَّ عَلَىٰ مَآ ءَاذَيْتُمُونَا ۚ وَعَلَى ٱللَّهِ فَلْيَتَوَكَّلِ ٱلْمُتَوَكِّلُونَ","translation":"And how could we not place our trust in God, seeing that it is He who has shown us the path which we are to follow? \"Hence, we shall certainly bear with patience whatever hurt you may do us: for, all who have trust [in His existence] must place their trust in God [alone]!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1762.mp3","surahId":14,"words":[{"id":14505,"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَا","translation":"এবং কি হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/014_012_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":14506,"position":2,"arabic":"لَنَآ","translation":"আমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/014_012_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":14507,"position":3,"arabic":"أَلَّا","translation":"যে না","audioUrl":"wbw/014_012_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":14508,"position":4,"arabic":"نَتَوَكَّلَ","translation":"আমরা ভরসা করবো","audioUrl":"wbw/014_012_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":14509,"position":5,"arabic":"عَلَى","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/014_012_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":14510,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/014_012_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":14511,"position":7,"arabic":"وَقَدْ","translation":"অথচ নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/014_012_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":14512,"position":8,"arabic":"هَدَىٰنَا","transla